## Prototype vs Full: FULL (richness 10)

Two integrated deliverables under slug `panhandle-garage-door-company`:
- **Part A:** Real WordPress site (Docker on Surface, port 8090) тАФ SEO-architected, 25+ pages, bespoke door-company design. Bridge clone from `maryland_driveway_wp_bridge_blueprint.py` (PORT 8081 -> 8090, PREFIX updated).
- **Part B:** SEO Analyzer тАФ existing GH Pages app at `https://mwegter95.github.io/free-seo-analyzer-with-js-rendering/`. Open signup already works (`POST /auth/register`, no verification, any fake email+password). WP site has a dedicated "Free SEO Audit" nav link and hero CTA linking to/embedding that app. **No rebuild. No new backend blueprint.**

