/hereford-tx/                            Deaf Smith County (feedlot/livestock = commercial overhead)
/canyon-tx/                              Randall County (growing Amarillo suburb)
/friona-tx/                              Parmer County (ag, border market)
/clovis-nm/                              Curry County NM (Cannon AFB = commercial angle)
/tucumcari-nm/                           Quay County NM (Route 66 commerce)
/clayton-nm/                             Union County NM (cattle ranch, zero competitor LPs)
--- Blog ---
/blog/                                   Blog hub
/blog/commercial-overhead-door-guide/    "How to Choose a Commercial Overhead Door for Texas Businesses"
--- Conversion ---
/estimate/                               CF7 estimate request form
/contact/                                Contact + phone + address + map
