## SEO content hooks by city (differentiation strategy)

Competitors (Overhead Door Co. Amarillo, Price Overhead, Willow Creek, Integrity) have **zero city landing pages** for towns outside Amarillo. Primary gap.

| City | Content angle |
|---|---|
| Dumas TX | HQ authority, full service range, "locally owned" |
| Amarillo TX | Volume market, compete on speed + commercial depth |
| Borger TX | Refinery/industrial тАФ commercial overhead + dock equipment |
| Hereford TX | Feedlot/livestock тАФ commercial overhead, roll-up, barn doors |
| Dalhart TX | Ranch/ag тАФ barn & agricultural doors, roll-up |
| Clovis NM | Cannon AFB тАФ commercial, roll-up, storefront; bilingual |
| Perryton TX | "Only local-focused door company" тАФ zero competitor LP |
| Pampa TX | Balanced residential + light commercial |
| Canyon TX | Growing suburb тАФ residential garage doors, entry doors |
| Friona TX | Ag community тАФ barn doors, roll-up, commercial |
| Tucumcari NM | Route 66 commerce тАФ storefront, commercial |
| Clayton NM | Cattle ranch тАФ barn, roll-up, agricultural |

Bilingual hook ("Se Habla Espa├▒ol") embedded in every city page тАФ differentiator vs. Amarillo competitors.

