## WP theme approach (custom PHP, no page builders)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `functions.php` | Enqueue fonts/styles/scripts, register menus. No closing `?>`. |
| `header.php` | Sticky nav: logo + click-to-call `(806) 316-5296` + "Get Estimate" orange CTA |
| `footer.php` | Address, phone, hours, service list (linked), city list (linked), trust badges |
| `front-page.php` | Homepage: hero + 8-service grid + service area map + trust bar |
| `page-service.php` | Service silo template тАФ schema markup, FAQ section, local CTA |
| `page-city.php` | City LP template тАФ geo-targeted H1, service list for that city, map |
| `page-commercial.php` | Commercial hub |
| `page-residential.php` | Residential hub |
| `page-estimate.php` | CF7 form: name, phone, email, service type (8 options), city, message |
| `page-seo-audit.php` | Free SEO audit CTA + iframe embed of `mwegter95.github.io/free-seo-analyzer` |
| `single.php` | Blog post |
| `page.php` | Generic fallback |

All runner scripts ASCII-only (CLAUDE.md hard rule). No `?>` in any PHP file.

**Plugin stack (lightweight, all free):**
- Yoast SEO тАФ sitemap, metadata, robots.txt, breadcrumbs, schema assist
- Contact Form 7 тАФ estimate + contact forms
- WP Super Cache тАФ CWV / speed
- Redirection тАФ 301 redirect management (Squarespace migration map)

