## Technical SEO checklist

| Item | Implementation |
|---|---|
| Meta title/description | Yoast SEO per page; pattern: "[Service] in [City] TX \| Dimitroff Door Repair" |
| H1/H2/H3 hierarchy | Enforced in each template |
| XML sitemap | Yoast auto-generates `/sitemap.xml` |
| Robots.txt | Yoast-managed; all service/city/blog pages crawlable |
| Internal linking | Service pages -> city pages + city pages -> service pages; footer nav both dimensions |
| 301 redirects | Redirection plugin; `redirects-doc.md` maps Squarespace -> WP URL patterns |
| Core Web Vitals | Minimal theme CSS, no render-blocking JS, WebP images, lazy-load, WP Super Cache |
| Mobile-first | CSS Grid/Flex, breakpoints 768px + 375px; mobile sticky call bar |
| HTTPS | Cloudflare tunnel handles |
| GSC / GA setup | Sticky admin guide page in WP with step-by-step instructions |
| Conversion tracking | CF7 thank-you page redirect for form submission goal in GA |

