## SEO Analyzer (Part B) тАФ existing infrastructure, zero rebuild

**What exists:**
- GH Pages app: `https://mwegter95.github.io/free-seo-analyzer-with-js-rendering/` тАФ full UI with sign-up, login, analyze
- Backend: `api.michaelwegter.com` (`/auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/seo/analyze`, `/seo/crawl`, `/seo/reports`)
- Open signup: any email + password, bcrypt-hashed, no verification тАФ requirement met

**Demo-builder instructions:**
- WP site nav: "Free SEO Audit" link in header nav
- `/free-seo-audit/` WP page: explain what the tool does + iframe embed OR prominent CTA button opening analyzer in new tab + pre-fill URL field with `dimitroffdoorrepair.com` demo URL if iframe supports it
- No new backend blueprint, no code changes to analyzer

**Demo flow (proposal reviewer experience):**
1. Browse WP site, click "Free SEO Audit" in nav
2. Lands on `/free-seo-audit/` page тАФ pitch for the SEO audit service
3. Clicks through to analyzer, registers with any fake email + password
4. Runs analysis on the live WP demo URL or `dimitroffdoorrepair.com`
5. Sees real scored analysis output тАФ demonstrates "SEO tooling I bring"

